{"words":[{"word":"septimont","count":3},{"word":"ephor","count":2},{"word":"modest","count":2},{"word":"augusta","count":2},{"word":"without","count":2},{"word":"nestor","count":1},{"word":"traveling","count":1},{"word":"poet","count":1},{"word":"rains","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"seem","count":1},{"word":"eager","count":1},{"word":"leave","count":1},{"word":"season","count":1},{"word":"curious","count":1},{"word":"allow","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"honor","count":1},{"word":"offer","count":1},{"word":"service","count":1},{"word":"champion","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"agon","count":1},{"word":"hear","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"ways","count":1},{"word":"perceive","count":1},{"word":"trusting","count":1},{"word":"senses","count":1},{"word":"habit","count":1},{"word":"natural","count":1},{"word":"expedience","count":1},{"word":"option","count":1},{"word":"truth","count":1},{"word":"told","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"gathering","count":1},{"word":"inspiration","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"epic","count":1},{"word":"protagonist","count":1},{"word":"none","count":1},{"word":"speak","count":1},{"word":"familiarity","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"tale","count":1},{"word":"soon","count":1},{"word":"written","count":1},{"word":"knowing","count":1},{"word":"walk","count":1},{"word":"alongside","count":1},{"word":"rarely","count":1},{"word":"benefits","count":1},{"word":"girl","count":1},{"word":"humble","count":1},{"word":"birth","count":1},{"word":"resonator","count":1},{"word":"talent","count":1},{"word":"commoner","count":1},{"word":"noble","count":1},{"word":"patronage","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"den","count":1},{"word":"wolves","count":1},{"word":"city","count":1},{"word":"rose","count":1},{"word":"eventually","count":1},{"word":"claimed","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"burning","count":1},{"word":"sun","count":1},{"word":"cloud","count":1},{"word":"dust","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I am Nestor, a traveling poet.","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"The rains in Septimont never seem eager to leave this season. So then...","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"If you are curious about the Ephor... then allow me to say that nothing would honor me more than to offer even a modest service to the Champion of the Great Agon.","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"To see and to hear are but two of the many ways to perceive. Trusting the senses is a habit, a natural expedience, but not the only option.","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"Truth be told, I've been gathering inspiration for my next epic, and its protagonist is none other than Augusta, the Ephor of Septimont.","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"That's why I speak of her with some familiarity.","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"I have a feeling your tale with her will soon be written. And knowing more about those who walk alongside you is rarely without its benefits.","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"Augusta—","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"A girl of humble birth, a Resonator of modest talent, a commoner without noble patronage. And yet from the den of wolves that is Septimont City, she rose, and eventually claimed her place.","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000},{"text":"Just like the burning sun was once a cloud of dust.","quest_name":"Rust, Sword and the Sun","quest_id":164000000}]}